metadata.name: Nude Kate 1/6
metadata.description:
Killer: Kate
Weapon: —Årockett pistol

Nude killer project is about our duality and masks that we know how to put on when we are with someone nearby. This is a statement and a call to be more attentive and sensitive to our closest people, to see not only what they want to show, but also what is hidden between the lines.

Author: Igor Reno
Size: 3840x5760x300dpi
